<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p><em>Image Source: Hong Kong Tourism Board</em></p>'=>'<p><em>Image Source: Hong Kong Tourism Board</em></p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Open daily | East Coast Boardwalk, North Point</p><p>For a tranquil escape from the city’s hustle, discover one of the newest gems in town – the East Coast Boardwalk and the sprawling East Coast Park Precinct. This newly opened waterfront promenade offers breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour, seamlessly connecting North Point to Quarry Bay.</p><p>Take a leisurely stroll along the harbourfront, explore the lush greenery of the park precinct, and enjoy the stunning sunset while marveling at the iconic skyline views from both sides of the harbour. Whether you’re snapping photos, soaking in the sea breeze, or simply unwinding, this is the ideal spot to recharge after a day at the jewellery show.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p><em>Image Source: Harbourfront Commission, Government Information Centre</em></p>'=>'<p><strong>時間與地點</strong>：每日開放 | 北角東岸海濱長廊</p><p>若想遠離城市喧囂，尋找一處寧靜之地，不妨探索城中最新亮點——東岸海濱長廊及廣闊的東岸公園區域。這新開幕的海濱長廊以維多利亞港的壯麗景色作背景，無縫連接北角與鰂魚涌。 </p><p>您可沿著海濱悠閒漫步，探索公園綠意盎然，欣賞兩岸天際線的醉人日落。無論是拍照、感受海風，還是單純放鬆，這裡都是珠寶展後充電的理想地點。 </p><p> </p><p> </p><p><em>Image Source: Harbourfront Commission, Government Information Centre</em></p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Open daily | Temple Street, Jordan</p><p>Dive into Hong Kong’s buzzing street culture at the iconic Temple Street Night Market. This lively marketplace offers a sensory feast, from street-side food stalls, to fortune tellers and street performances.</p><p>Indulge in authentic Hong Kong delicacies, take in the vibrant atmosphere of this quintessential local experience. It’s a vibrant slice of Hong Kong’s heartbeat - fantastic way to immerse yourself in this city’s dynamic street culture. Don’t forget to pick up some one-of-a-kind treasures as souvenirs to take home!</p>'=>'<p><strong>時間與地點</strong>：每日開放 | 佐敦廟街</p><p>走進香港充滿活力的街頭文化，體驗標誌性的廟街夜市。從街頭美食攤檔到算命師及街頭表演，應有盡有。 </p><p>您可品嚐正宗香港美食，沉浸於熱鬧氣氛，這是香港脈動的生動縮影。別忘了挑選一些獨一無二的紀念品，帶回家留念喔！  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until April 13, 2025 | AIRSIDE, Kai Tak</p><p><strong>Calling all movie buffs!</strong> This immersive exhibition takes you back in time with a meticulously restored film set from the classic “Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In”.</p><p>Walk through authenic locations from the movie scenes, like a barber shop, tea stall, and bone-setting clinic, all painstakingly designed to capture the gritty charm of old Hong Kong. You’ll also get a behind-the-scences look at the craftsmanship and artistry that went into the movie’s production, as well as insights into Hong Kong’s rich film history and the legendary Kowloon Walled City. It’s a nostalgic journey into Hong Kong’s cinematic soul – a great way to experience the spirit of the city.</p>'=>'<p><strong>時間與地點</strong>：即日起至2025年4月13日 | 啟德AIRSIDE</p><p><strong>影迷注意！</strong> 此沉浸式展覽將帶您穿越時空，回到經典電影《九龍城寨之圍城》中精心復原的拍攝場景。</p><p>您可漫步於電影中真實再現的場景，如理髮店、茶檔及跌打醫館，感受舊香港的粗獷魅力。此外，您更有機會一窺電影製作的幕後工藝與藝術，深入了解香港豐富的電影歷史以及傳奇九龍城寨的背景故事。這是一場探索香港電影靈魂的懷舊之旅，讓您親身感受這座城市的獨特文化氣息。  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until March 2, 2025 | Lee Tung Avenue, Wan Chai</p><p>Step into a magical wonderland at <a href="https://www.leetungavenue.com.hk/en/index/">Lee Tung Avenue</a>, where over 800 traditional Chinese lanterns cast a warm glow across this tree-lined pedestrian avenue in celebration of the Year of the Snake. Glowing in hues of gold and red - symbolizing happiness and prosperity – the lanterns create a serene and enchanting vibe, perfect for an evening stroll.</p><p>Don’t miss the peach blossom garden with its charming heart-shaped arch – an ideal spot for Instagrammable photos! This is the ultimate place to soak in the festive ambiance after a busy day at the jewellery show. Plus, who doesn’t love a bit of good fortune and blessings under the glow of lanterns?</p>'=>'<p><strong>時間與地點</strong>：即日起至2025年3月2日 | 灣仔利東街</p><p>走進<a href="https://www.leetungavenue.com.hk/en/index/">利東街</a>，彷彿置身奇幻仙境。這條綠樹成蔭的步行街懸掛超過800盞傳統中式燈籠，為慶祝蛇年而點亮溫暖光芒。 </p><p>別錯過桃花園中迷人的心形拱門，那是拍攝網紅照片的絕佳地點！在珠寶展忙碌一天後，這裡是感受節日氣氛的最佳場所。誰能抗拒在燈籠輝映下祈求好運與祝福的美好時刻呢？  </p>','<p><strong>When &amp; Where:</strong> Until March 6, 2025 | Central Market, Central</p><p><strong>Attention panda lovers!</strong> This whimsical festival is a must-see. With over 800 panda sculptures featuring festive Lunar New Year designs scattered across Central Market. It’s a creative and adorable celebration of Hong Kong’s panda craze.</p><p>But that’s not all! Make time to visit <a href="https://www.oceanpark.com.hk/">Ocean Park</a>, where you can meet the beloved panda twins and the two newly added family members. It’s a moment of pure joy and relaxation that’s perfect for escaping the hustle and bustle of the jewellery show.</p>'=>'<p><strong>時間與地點</strong>：即日起至2025年3月6日 | 中環街市</p><p><strong>熊貓愛好者注意！</strong> 這個充滿趣味的活動不容錯過。中環街市遍佈超過800個以農曆新年為主題的熊貓雕塑，展現香港對熊貓的熱愛。  </p><p>此外，不妨抽空前往<a href="https://www.oceanpark.com.hk/">海洋公園</a>，探訪深受喜愛的熊貓雙胞胎及其兩個新加入的家庭成員。這是遠離珠寶展喧囂、享受純粹快樂與放鬆的完美選擇。  </p>','<p>As you gear up for the <strong>Hong Kong International Jewellery Show</strong> (March 4-8, 2025), why not add an extra sparkle to your itinerary? Beyond the brilliance of gems and countless business opportunities, Hong Kong is a city bursting with cultural, treasures, scenic spots, and unique experiences that will make your visit truly unforgettable.</p><p>We’ve handpicked<strong> five incredible must-visit places and events</strong> happening during your stay. Whether you’re seeking inspiration, or just some fun, there’s something on this list for everyone – perfect for unwinding after a productive day at the jewellery show.</p><p><strong>Ready to explore? Let’s dive in!</strong></p>'=>'<p>您準備好參加2025年3月4日至8日舉行的<strong>香港國際珠寶展</strong>了嗎？除了展會上琳琅滿目的珠寶與無數商機，香港這座城市還充滿文化寶藏、風景名勝和獨特體驗，定能為您的旅程增添難忘回憶。 </p><p>我們為您精心挑選了<strong>5個不容錯過的景點和活動</strong>，讓您在繁忙的展會以外，盡情感受香港魅力。無論您想尋找靈感還是輕鬆一下，這份清單都能滿足您的需求，助您在珠寶展結束後好好放鬆。 </p><p><strong>您準備好了嗎？ </strong></p>','<p>These five unforgettable experiences are the perfect complement to your time during the <a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/en"><strong>Hong Kong International Jewellery Show 2025</strong></a>. From the glowing lanterns to the cinematic nostalgia and iconic street markets, each spot offers a unique taste of Hong Kong’s culture and creativity.</p><p>So, pack your bags, polish your business cards, and prepare for a trip filled with dazzling gems – both at the jewellery show and across the city. Which experience will you choose first? Let us know in the comments or tag us in your Hong Kong travel highlights!</p><p>Don’t forget to visit us to explore our fabulous new collections and experience our exceptional bespoke services. It is also a perfect opportunity to share your discoveries and insights from your visits.</p>'=>'<p>以上5個難忘體驗，與<a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/tc"><strong>香港國際珠寶展</strong></a>相得益彰。從燈籠輝映的節日氣氛到電影懷舊之旅，再到標誌性的街頭夜市，每個地點都展現了香港獨特的文化與創意。 </p><p>收拾好行李，準備好名片，為這場充滿璀璨珠寶與城市魅力的旅程做好準備吧！  </p><p>您會先選擇哪個體驗？歡迎在評論中告訴我們，或在您的香港之旅中標記我們，分享您的精彩時刻！ </p>','<p>📅</p><p>    MARCH 4 (TUE)           1030-1830</p><p>MARCH 5-7 (WED-FRI)     1000-1830</p><p class="last-child">     MARCH 8 (SAT)           1000-1730</p>'=>'<p>📅</p><p> 3月4日（二）10:30am – 6:30pm</p><p>3月5日～7日（三～五）10am – 6:30pm</p><p class="last-child"> 3月8日（六）10am – 5:30pm</p>','<p>📍</p><p><strong>WORLD OF GLAMOUR HALL 1C #C02</strong></p><p>HONG KONG CONVENTION AND EXHIBITION CENTRE</p><p>1 EXPO DRIVE</p><p class="last-child">WAN CHAI, HONG KONG</p>'=>'<p>📍</p><p><strong>瑰麗珠寶館 1C廳 #C02</strong></p><p>香港會議展覽中心</p><p>灣仔博覽道一號</p><p class="last-child">香港</p>','Hong Kong International Jewellery Show 2025'=>'香港國際珠寶展','Image Source: Instagram @pandago_fest'=>'Image Source: Instagram @pandago_fest','Image Source: Lee Tung Avenue'=>'Image Source: Lee Tung Avenue','Lee Tung Avenue: “Lanterns-Lit Year of the Snake”'=>'利東街：元宵節燈籠展','Panda Go! Fest 